init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The mug, which had always read "#1 Dad" suddenly changed to "#4 Dad."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Dad, I just pulled out my "#1 Dad" mug and it changed to "#4 Dad."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: he said, "Oh, I'm sorry, son, but I've been demoted."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The next day I pulled out my mug and it had changed to "#5 Dad."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I called my dad and he said, "I'm sorry, son, but I guess you've been demoted again."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I played with my kids, I took them to the park, I helped them with their homework, I even went to the grocery store with my wife

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The next morning I pulled out my mug and it had changed to "#6 Dad."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I would do whatever it took to get back to #1.
